1
00:01:09,200 --> 00:01:10,200
I didn't kill him.

2
00:01:12,200 --> 00:01:13,130
When I got there,

3
00:01:14,080 --> 00:01:15,210
he was already dead.

4
00:01:15,760 --> 00:01:16,690
What did you say?

5
00:01:18,680 --> 00:01:20,010
On the night of the 25th,

6
00:01:36,200 --> 00:01:37,330
he was already dead.

7
00:01:37,880 --> 00:01:40,479
Clean it up. Don't let the police get involved.

8
00:01:40,680 --> 00:01:41,039
Okay.

9
00:01:59,720 --> 00:02:02,180
So you dismembered the body in the bathroom?

10
00:02:06,960 --> 00:02:08,690
Why did you dismember the body?

11
00:02:12,400 --> 00:02:14,860
I really didn't want to deal with you people.

12
00:02:16,040 --> 00:02:17,170
He was already dead.

13
00:02:18,640 --> 00:02:20,500
I was afraid you would suspect me,

14
00:02:21,000 --> 00:02:22,840
so I disposed of the body.

15
00:02:25,480 --> 00:02:27,410
Who is it? What are you doing there?

16
00:02:28,200 --> 00:02:28,640
Me.

17
00:02:29,160 --> 00:02:29,960
Manager Chen.

18
00:02:30,040 --> 00:02:31,360
What are you doing there?

19
00:02:31,360 --> 00:02:32,290
Moving some dirt

20
00:02:32,480 --> 00:02:33,810
to weigh down the rebar.

21
00:02:33,840 --> 00:02:35,170
There's a big pit ahead.

22
00:02:35,440 --> 00:02:36,640
I'm filling it with dirt.

23
00:02:36,640 --> 00:02:37,500
Let me help you.

24
00:02:37,520 --> 00:02:38,079
No need.

25
00:02:38,440 --> 00:02:39,300
Go do your work.

26
00:02:39,920 --> 00:02:41,850
Okay, we'll wait for you in the car.

27
00:02:41,920 --> 00:02:42,480
Go.

28
00:03:00,280 --> 00:03:02,340
How can you prove you didn't kill him?

29
00:03:05,160 --> 00:03:07,000
You've already been to my place, right?

30
00:03:07,000 --> 00:03:10,080
There's a solid black lighter.

31
00:03:10,680 --> 00:03:12,810
You must have brought it back already.

32
00:03:16,480 --> 00:03:17,240
Whose is this?

33
00:03:17,240 --> 00:03:18,640
It was left by the killer.

34
00:03:18,920 --> 00:03:19,640
At the time,

35
00:03:21,400 --> 00:03:23,260
it was right by Tian Liang's feet.

36
00:03:31,079 --> 00:03:34,200
Does this count as redeeming myself?

37
00:03:36,000 --> 00:03:36,460
Mr. Jin.

38
00:03:37,600 --> 00:03:38,060
Mr. Jin.

39
00:03:39,120 --> 00:03:39,579
Mr. Jin.

40
00:03:41,120 --> 00:03:42,079
Um...

41
00:03:42,280 --> 00:03:42,920
Mr. Jin.

42
00:03:44,079 --> 00:03:46,079
Can't you two sit down and rest a bit?

43
00:03:46,160 --> 00:03:48,200
What's the use of calling me all the time?

44
00:03:48,200 --> 00:03:49,800
We finally got this clue.

45
00:03:49,920 --> 00:03:50,680
This DNA result

46
00:03:50,680 --> 00:03:52,010
is very important to us.

47
00:03:52,120 --> 00:03:53,120
All right, I know.

48
00:03:53,280 --> 00:03:55,079
No, when will the results be out?

49
00:03:55,600 --> 00:03:56,280
Mr. Jin.

50
00:03:57,760 --> 00:03:58,360
Answer me.

51
00:03:58,440 --> 00:03:59,240
Wait a minute.

52
00:04:01,040 --> 00:04:02,170
The results are out.

53
00:04:02,920 --> 00:04:03,760
It's confirmed

54
00:04:03,760 --> 00:04:05,820
that the bloodstain is Tian Liang's.

55
00:04:07,760 --> 00:04:08,360
Great.

56
00:04:08,600 --> 00:04:09,880
We can finally confirm that place

57
00:04:09,880 --> 00:04:11,410
is the primary crime scene.

58
00:04:12,040 --> 00:04:13,840
The lighter has been handed over to forensics

59
00:04:13,840 --> 00:04:15,160
to see if there are any useful clues.

60
00:04:15,160 --> 00:04:16,600
That house is under Xia Lin's name.

61
00:04:16,600 --> 00:04:17,920
We can interrogate those three now.

62
00:04:17,920 --> 00:04:18,680
Thanks, Lao Jin.

63
00:04:18,680 --> 00:04:20,120
You did a great job, Lao Jin.

64
00:04:20,120 --> 00:04:20,560
Thank you.

65
00:04:20,560 --> 00:04:21,560
Hurry, hurry.

66
00:04:25,120 --> 00:04:26,360
On the night of July 25th,

67
00:04:26,360 --> 00:04:27,490
what were you doing?

68
00:04:27,560 --> 00:04:28,880
July 25th

69
00:04:28,880 --> 00:04:30,120
was Xiaoyun's birthday.

70
00:04:30,120 --> 00:04:32,320
We were at home celebrating her birthday.

71
00:04:32,320 --> 00:04:33,320
Until 11 o'clock,

72
00:04:33,520 --> 00:04:34,580
neither of us left.

73
00:04:35,159 --> 00:04:36,040
With Ye Qiming?

74
00:04:37,400 --> 00:04:37,760
Yes.

75
00:04:38,840 --> 00:04:39,700
Huang Xiaoyun,

76
00:04:40,200 --> 00:04:42,659
what were you doing on the night of July 25th?

77
00:04:42,800 --> 00:04:43,400
At home.

78
00:04:44,000 --> 00:04:46,680
Uncle Ye and Aunt Xia were celebrating my birthday.

79
00:04:46,680 --> 00:04:47,880
Do you have any proof?

80
00:04:47,880 --> 00:04:48,400
Yes.

81
00:04:48,880 --> 00:04:50,880
I took photos and videos at the time.

82
00:04:51,040 --> 00:04:52,640
I'll bring them to you later.

83
00:04:52,920 --> 00:04:53,320
Okay.

84
00:04:53,600 --> 00:04:55,930
Make sure to give us the videos and photos.

85
00:04:56,040 --> 00:04:56,520
Okay.

86
00:04:57,120 --> 00:04:59,250
Why didn't Lu Yang go to your birthday?

87
00:05:00,520 --> 00:05:02,640
He took me out for lunch.

88
00:05:03,320 --> 00:05:05,000
He doesn't really like Uncle Ye,

89
00:05:05,000 --> 00:05:06,240
so he wasn't invited.

90
00:05:06,800 --> 00:05:08,440
Was Lu Yang at school in the afternoon?

91
00:05:08,440 --> 00:05:08,800
Yes.

92
00:05:09,200 --> 00:05:11,400
We left school together in the evening.

93
00:05:12,440 --> 00:05:14,040
Do you recognize this house?

94
00:05:14,440 --> 00:05:15,100
No, I don't.

95
00:05:15,720 --> 00:05:16,850
This is not my house.

96
00:05:17,160 --> 00:05:18,820
Tian Liang died in this house.

97
00:05:19,440 --> 00:05:20,240
I didn't know.

98
00:05:20,920 --> 00:05:22,680
This house is under Xia Lin's name.

99
00:05:22,680 --> 00:05:24,760
We suspect Xia Lin is connected to Tian Liang's death.

100
00:05:24,760 --> 00:05:25,890
That's impossible.

101
00:05:26,040 --> 00:05:27,040
Xia Lin is so weak.

102
00:05:27,040 --> 00:05:27,640
And that day,

103
00:05:27,640 --> 00:05:29,440
we were together the whole time.

104
00:05:38,840 --> 00:05:39,840
These statements

105
00:05:41,040 --> 00:05:42,040
are flawless.

106
00:05:42,640 --> 00:05:45,170
None of the three had time to commit the crime.

107
00:05:45,880 --> 00:05:47,540
Ye Qiming even firmly insists

108
00:05:48,360 --> 00:05:50,680
that he doesn't even know about that house.

109
00:05:50,680 --> 00:05:52,940
Why do I feel like something isn't right?

110
00:05:53,560 --> 00:05:56,220
Isn't Ye Qiming keeping himself a bit too clean?

111
00:05:58,159 --> 00:05:58,960
Fortunately,

112
00:05:59,400 --> 00:06:02,400
we've found the dismemberment scene and the culprit.

113
00:06:02,680 --> 00:06:04,610
We are getting closer to the truth.

114
00:06:32,159 --> 00:06:32,560
Hello.

115
00:06:33,200 --> 00:06:33,880
Who is this?

116
00:06:34,960 --> 00:06:35,520
It's me.

117
00:06:36,320 --> 00:06:36,920
Mr. Ye.

118
00:06:37,920 --> 00:06:38,440
What?

119
00:06:39,480 --> 00:06:40,740
You want to cooperate?

120
00:06:41,320 --> 00:06:41,980
Let's talk.

121
00:06:42,440 --> 00:06:44,970
It seems you don't have any leverage right now

122
00:06:45,080 --> 00:06:46,720
to negotiate with me.

123
00:06:47,120 --> 00:06:50,159
I can't believe you're in this situation

124
00:06:50,600 --> 00:06:51,730
and still so greedy.

125
00:06:52,520 --> 00:06:53,520
You know,

126
00:06:54,000 --> 00:06:56,800
those who go against me never end well.

127
00:06:57,480 --> 00:06:58,720
Total disregard for human life.

128
00:06:58,720 --> 00:06:59,450
I've seen it.

129
00:07:00,560 --> 00:07:02,760
Like that female reporter.

130
00:07:03,600 --> 00:07:06,000
You had a hand in that too.

131
00:07:06,880 --> 00:07:08,210
Once you're in the game,

132
00:07:08,240 --> 00:07:12,000
I'm afraid you can't walk away clean.

133
00:07:12,640 --> 00:07:14,370
Maybe I don't want to walk away.

134
00:07:15,720 --> 00:07:17,600
After all, you gave me no way out

135
00:07:18,520 --> 00:07:20,120
and dragged my son into this.

136
00:07:21,240 --> 00:07:22,570
Are you threatening me?

137
00:07:23,960 --> 00:07:25,480
You threatened me first.

138
00:07:26,400 --> 00:07:27,400
Do you believe

139
00:07:27,960 --> 00:07:29,200
I can have you killed?

140
00:07:30,440 --> 00:07:32,900
I have nothing to lose in a fight to the death.

141
00:07:33,120 --> 00:07:33,560
You...

142
00:07:34,960 --> 00:07:36,490
I will use those documents.

143
00:07:37,480 --> 00:07:39,340
In exchange for my son's freedom,

144
00:07:40,080 --> 00:07:42,280
is this deal worth it?

145
00:07:43,040 --> 00:07:43,700
You decide.

146
00:07:48,840 --> 00:07:50,040
The project in the eastern suburbs,

147
00:07:50,040 --> 00:07:51,370
I'll help you secure it.

148
00:07:53,400 --> 00:07:54,640
Your Tongda Group

149
00:07:54,840 --> 00:07:57,840
will definitely be jumping over the dragon gate.

150
00:08:13,680 --> 00:08:14,480
Who let you in?

151
00:08:15,120 --> 00:08:16,580
Didn't you order the wine?

152
00:08:19,960 --> 00:08:21,240
Let me check the order.

153
00:08:25,520 --> 00:08:26,640
This waiter

154
00:08:27,520 --> 00:08:28,850
looks very unfamiliar.

155
00:08:35,640 --> 00:08:36,440
Let me.

156
00:08:38,480 --> 00:08:40,000
We didn't order wine. You made a mistake.

157
00:08:40,000 --> 00:08:41,260
Please leave quickly.

158
00:08:41,320 --> 00:08:42,720
I'm sorry.

159
00:08:58,760 --> 00:09:00,690
The waiter brought the wrong wine.

160
00:09:01,920 --> 00:09:02,850
Let's continue.

161
00:09:03,560 --> 00:09:05,680
Our group can't afford any mistakes right now.

162
00:09:05,680 --> 00:09:06,240
Mr. Ye.

163
00:09:08,000 --> 00:09:09,200
Illegally transferring ten million yuan

164
00:09:09,200 --> 00:09:10,600
will get you in jail, son.

165
00:09:10,880 --> 00:09:12,160
Yu Na won't lie to me.

166
00:09:12,600 --> 00:09:13,160
Son,

167
00:09:13,480 --> 00:09:14,280
listen to Dad.

168
00:09:14,880 --> 00:09:17,600
Yu Na is definitely not the kind of person you think she is.

169
00:09:17,600 --> 00:09:18,840
You guys stay out of it.

170
00:09:18,840 --> 00:09:19,600
I know what I'm doing.

171
00:09:19,600 --> 00:09:20,680
Son, listen to me.

172
00:09:30,520 --> 00:09:32,180
He is very confused right now.

173
00:09:32,240 --> 00:09:34,240
He won't listen to anything you say.

174
00:09:34,960 --> 00:09:35,600
I'm here.

175
00:09:35,840 --> 00:09:37,840
I'll figure something out with you.

176
00:09:49,760 --> 00:09:51,560
I just feel that for so many years,

177
00:09:51,560 --> 00:09:52,960
I've really let you down.

178
00:09:55,240 --> 00:09:56,570
Why are you saying this?

179
00:09:59,080 --> 00:10:00,810
We still have a long life ahead.

180
00:10:01,040 --> 00:10:02,570
Take good care of yourself.

181
00:10:03,680 --> 00:10:05,210
What are you talking about?

182
00:10:05,600 --> 00:10:06,720
Aren't you here?

183
00:10:06,960 --> 00:10:09,020
Didn't you promise to take care of me?

184
00:10:13,600 --> 00:10:14,460
How about this?

185
00:10:17,560 --> 00:10:18,200
Tonight,

186
00:10:19,920 --> 00:10:21,650
I want to invite Yu Na to dinner.

187
00:10:22,440 --> 00:10:24,970
Ye Yuan's matter can't be delayed any longer.

188
00:10:26,280 --> 00:10:27,680
Then let's have her over.

189
00:10:28,480 --> 00:10:29,480
I'll go get ready.

190
00:10:49,920 --> 00:10:52,120
All the evidence points to this Chen Hao.

191
00:10:52,120 --> 00:10:54,040
But he keeps saying he didn't kill anyone.

192
00:10:54,040 --> 00:10:55,200
He said when he got there,

193
00:10:55,200 --> 00:10:56,800
Tian Liang was already dead.

194
00:10:56,840 --> 00:10:57,920
Right now, we can't find

195
00:10:57,920 --> 00:10:59,780
a third person's DNA at the scene.

196
00:11:00,200 --> 00:11:01,280
The only evidence we have

197
00:11:01,280 --> 00:11:02,520
is that lighter.

198
00:11:02,960 --> 00:11:05,420
We must find everyone related to the lighter

199
00:11:06,160 --> 00:11:07,220
so we can figure out

200
00:11:07,480 --> 00:11:09,340
whether Chen Hao is just stalling

201
00:11:09,560 --> 00:11:10,800
or he really didn't kill him.

202
00:11:10,800 --> 00:11:13,330
The fingerprint match for the lighter is out.

203
00:11:13,520 --> 00:11:14,040
Kuai.

204
00:11:14,640 --> 00:11:15,080
Previously,

205
00:11:15,080 --> 00:11:17,360
he committed intentional injury at Jiangbei Club.

206
00:11:17,360 --> 00:11:19,840
He was sentenced to seven years and just released three months ago.

207
00:11:19,840 --> 00:11:21,970
His fingerprints are in the database.

208
00:11:22,840 --> 00:11:23,700
Captain Jiang.

209
00:11:24,600 --> 00:11:25,730
I handled this case.

210
00:11:27,800 --> 00:11:28,800
I know where he is.

211
00:11:31,960 --> 00:11:34,360
You just got out and want to go back in again?

212
00:11:38,320 --> 00:11:40,040
Do you have anything else to explain?

213
00:11:40,040 --> 00:11:41,640
What is there for me to explain?

214
00:11:41,640 --> 00:11:42,700
I got caught by you,

215
00:11:43,160 --> 00:11:44,000
so that's it.

216
00:11:44,440 --> 00:11:47,100
What deep hatred do you have against Tian Liang?

217
00:11:47,680 --> 00:11:48,960
To be specific,

218
00:11:49,680 --> 00:11:51,280
there's no deep hatred.

219
00:11:51,880 --> 00:11:53,960
But I just knew he wasn't a good guy.

220
00:11:54,200 --> 00:11:56,960
I mainly took money to do things for people.

221
00:11:57,400 --> 00:11:58,660
Who gave you the money?

222
00:11:59,040 --> 00:12:00,840
The boss of Tongda Company,

223
00:12:02,000 --> 00:12:03,280
Ye Qiming.

224
00:12:05,000 --> 00:12:06,130
Tell me the details.

225
00:12:16,640 --> 00:12:17,160
Not bad.

226
00:12:19,280 --> 00:12:19,740
For you.

227
00:12:20,400 --> 00:12:21,660
I quit smoking anyway.

228
00:12:26,000 --> 00:12:26,960
Get the job done,

229
00:12:27,600 --> 00:12:29,060
and you'll get your money.

230
00:12:33,080 --> 00:12:34,520
Use Tian Liang's phone

231
00:12:34,640 --> 00:12:36,520
to send that message to this person.

232
00:12:36,520 --> 00:12:37,250
Don't worry.

233
00:12:37,760 --> 00:12:38,560
Your business

234
00:12:39,480 --> 00:12:40,560
is all in my head.

235
00:12:42,040 --> 00:12:42,840
Leave it to me.

236
00:12:50,640 --> 00:12:51,970
Did you bring the stuff?

237
00:13:00,720 --> 00:13:01,850
Where are the goods?

238
00:13:33,040 --> 00:13:34,600
Welcome to our home, Yuna.

239
00:13:43,680 --> 00:13:44,940
What? Afraid to drink?

240
00:13:45,800 --> 00:13:47,060
Afraid it's poisoned?

241
00:13:49,760 --> 00:13:50,560
Come on, wife.

242
00:13:50,880 --> 00:13:51,940
Let's have a toast.

243
00:13:58,160 --> 00:13:58,760
Let's eat.

244
00:13:58,760 --> 00:13:59,200
Okay.

245
00:14:00,200 --> 00:14:01,120
I never thought

246
00:14:01,680 --> 00:14:03,680
we could still eat at the same table.

247
00:14:07,720 --> 00:14:11,120
Maybe I'll even have to call you mother-in-law in the future.

248
00:14:19,960 --> 00:14:21,880
Let's have a toast as a family.

249
00:14:24,840 --> 00:14:26,480
Come, Xiaoyun.

250
00:14:28,280 --> 00:14:29,560
Come, dear.

251
00:14:30,560 --> 00:14:32,890
Let's drink together as a family of three.

252
00:14:44,080 --> 00:14:44,600
Yu Na,

253
00:14:45,920 --> 00:14:46,720
I asked you to come here today

254
00:14:46,720 --> 00:14:48,040
to talk about Ye Yuan.

255
00:14:49,480 --> 00:14:50,200
You know,

256
00:14:50,760 --> 00:14:51,440
my target

257
00:14:51,680 --> 00:14:52,720
was never Ye Yuan.

258
00:14:54,640 --> 00:14:56,280
I don't care about anything else.

259
00:14:56,280 --> 00:14:58,320
As long as you leave Ye Yuan out of this

260
00:14:58,320 --> 00:14:59,920
and let my friend pick him up,

261
00:15:00,040 --> 00:15:01,880
the controlling stake of my company

262
00:15:01,880 --> 00:15:02,680
will be yours.

263
00:15:05,880 --> 00:15:08,210
We wouldn't be here if you said so earlier.

264
00:15:12,560 --> 00:15:14,020
Let them take Ye Yuan away.

265
00:15:29,640 --> 00:15:31,300
I'm not the one pestering him.

266
00:15:35,400 --> 00:15:36,160
Don't worry.

267
00:15:36,440 --> 00:15:37,500
I'm not interested

268
00:15:37,880 --> 00:15:38,600
in a kid.

269
00:15:43,760 --> 00:15:44,600
Shameless.

270
00:15:53,400 --> 00:15:53,840
Yu Na.

271
00:15:54,760 --> 00:15:55,200
Yu Na.

272
00:15:56,120 --> 00:15:56,560
Yu Na.

273
00:16:00,840 --> 00:16:01,920
You can still stop

274
00:16:02,040 --> 00:16:03,240
before it's too late.

275
00:16:03,400 --> 00:16:04,320
All I want

276
00:16:05,760 --> 00:16:06,480
is you.

277
00:16:19,400 --> 00:16:19,800
Yu Na.
